@startuml RouteCreationSequence
actor User
participant Frontend
participant API
database DB
User -> Frontend: Initiate Create Route
Frontend -> API: POST /routes {payload}
API -> API: Validate + authorize (tenant, role)
API -> DB: BEGIN TX
API -> DB: Insert Route
API -> DB: Insert Stops (loop)
DB --> API: Commit OK
API --> Frontend: 201 Created {routeId}
Frontend -> API: (optional) POST /routes/{id}/optimize
API --> Frontend: 202 Accepted (future async)
@enduml
